{"title":"“万诗乡”诗选","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万诗乡”诗选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者按：河北省丰润县东田庄乡在今年9月初掀起了一个群众性的写诗运动，会写的动手，不会写的动口，真是人人作诗个个歌唱，不到半月，就把这个乡变成了“万诗乡”。这里选登了几首。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥如积金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥如积金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造肥如造金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料上到地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地变聚宝盆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张宝贵）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争上游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古时作诗讲风流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝作诗讲丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革新学文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放思想争上游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张云祥）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修起沼气站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽灯家家安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群星移地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堂到人间。（郑洪树、张复生）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快速磨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石磨滚珠化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用牲口拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏转如飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨盘落雪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（大老崔）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送公粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胖胖麦儿库里藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满满袋儿车上装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣红马儿车上套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶着车儿送公粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（张复生）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是第一次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民办大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇孺皆作诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史五千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是第一次。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（李志国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂妇女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天忙在家里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天忙在地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天忙在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要跟男子汉比比高低。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薅草是健将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥是大将，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打水是啥将？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要跟男子汉较量较量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（新）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}